          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Improving Rural Access to Power Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill authorizes Federal Home Loan Banks to purchase certain securities from cooperatives that (1)&nbsp;have certain investment experience involving the Rural Utilities Service, and (2) have received financing from the Federal Financing Bank. </p>]]></text>
